🛒 E-Commerce Customer Analysis

This project presents a comprehensive SQL-based analysis of an e-commerce customer dataset.
It uncovers insights into customer behavior, revenue patterns, satisfaction levels, and marketing effectiveness.

📊 Dataset Overview

The dataset includes detailed customer-level information:

Attributes:

Gender
Customer Segment
Annual Income
CustomerID
Quantity & Unit Price
Revenue & Profit Margin
Customer Satisfaction
Loyalty Score
Purchase Frequency
Purchase Quarter
Weekend Indicator (Is_Weekend)
Days to Next Purchase
Season
Marketing Channel
First Purchase Channel

Dataset Size:

👥 Total Customers: 47,926
👨 Male: 23,888 (~49.8%)
👩 Female: 24,038 (~50.2%)
